{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":120,"text":"So I'm going to talk about trust,"},{"time":2215,"text":"and I'm going to start by reminding you"},{"time":4495,"text":"of the standard views that people have about trust."},{"time":8576,"text":"I think these are so commonplace,"},{"time":10815,"text":"they've become clich√©s of our society."},{"time":13103,"text":"And I think there are three."},{"time":15129,"text":"One's a claim: there has been a great decline in trust,"},{"time":19961,"text":"very widely believed."},{"time":21869,"text":"The second is an aim: we should have more trust."},{"time":26376,"text":"And the third is a task: we should rebuild trust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31866,"text":"I think that the claim, the aim and the task"},{"time":36204,"text":"are all misconceived."},{"time":38374,"text":"So what I'm going to try to tell you today"},{"time":40023,"text":"is a different story about a claim, an aim and a task"},{"time":44713,"text":"which I think give one quite a lot better purchase on the matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49340,"text":"First the claim: Why do people think trust has declined?"},{"time":54106,"text":"And if I really think about it on the basis of my own evidence,"},{"time":57907,"text":"I don't know the answer."},{"time":59681,"text":"I'm inclined to think it may have declined"},{"time":63490,"text":"in some activities or some institutions"},{"time":66996,"text":"and it might have grown in others."},{"time":68800,"text":"I don't have an overview."},{"time":70744,"text":"But, of course, I can look at the opinion polls,"},{"time":75081,"text":"and the opinion polls are supposedly"},{"time":77449,"text":"the source of a belief that trust has declined."},{"time":81401,"text":"When you actually look at opinion polls across time,"},{"time":85258,"text":"there's not much evidence for that."},{"time":87056,"text":"That's to say, the people who were mistrusted"},{"time":89646,"text":"20 years ago,"},{"time":91257,"text":"principally journalists and politicians, are still mistrusted."},{"time":95810,"text":"And the people who were highly trusted 20 years ago"},{"time":99180,"text":"are still rather highly trusted: judges, nurses."},{"time":102625,"text":"The rest of us are in between,"},{"time":104529,"text":"and by the way, the average person in the street"},{"time":107599,"text":"is almost exactly midway."},{"time":109623,"text":"But is that good evidence?"},{"time":111856,"text":"What opinion polls record is, of course, opinions."},{"time":116012,"text":"What else can they record?"},{"time":117579,"text":"So they're looking at the generic attitudes"},{"time":121120,"text":"that people report when you ask them certain questions."},{"time":124659,"text":"Do you trust politicians? Do you trust teachers?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128589,"text":"Now if somebody said to you, \"Do you trust greengrocers?"},{"time":132221,"text":"Do you trust fishmongers?"},{"time":134118,"text":"Do you trust elementary school teachers?\""},{"time":136750,"text":"you would probably begin by saying, \"To do what?\""},{"time":140341,"text":"And that would be a perfectly sensible response."},{"time":143555,"text":"And you might say, when you understood the answer to that,"},{"time":148680,"text":"\"Well, I trust some of them, but not others.\""},{"time":152120,"text":"That's a perfectly rational thing."},{"time":154038,"text":"In short, in our real lives,"},{"time":157160,"text":"we seek to place trust in a differentiated way."},{"time":160810,"text":"We don't make an assumption that the level of trust"},{"time":164386,"text":"that we will have in every instance of a certain type"},{"time":167882,"text":"of official or office-holder or type of person"},{"time":171797,"text":"is going to be uniform."},{"time":173742,"text":"I might, for example, say that I certainly trust"},{"time":177465,"text":"a certain elementary school teacher I know"},{"time":179910,"text":"to teach the reception class to read,"},{"time":182536,"text":"but in no way to drive the school minibus."},{"time":186184,"text":"I might, after all, know that she wasn't a good driver."},{"time":189285,"text":"I might trust my most loquacious friend"},{"time":192562,"text":"to keep a conversation going"},{"time":194654,"text":"but not -- but perhaps not to keep a secret."},{"time":204313,"text":"Simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205562,"text":"So if we've got those evidence in our ordinary lives"},{"time":210468,"text":"of the way that trust is differentiated,"},{"time":212584,"text":"why do we sort of drop all that intelligence"},{"time":215835,"text":"when we think about trust more abstractly?"},{"time":219458,"text":"I think the polls are very bad guides"},{"time":222202,"text":"to the level of trust that actually exists,"},{"time":225259,"text":"because they try to obliterate the good judgment"},{"time":228831,"text":"that goes into placing trust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232238,"text":"Secondly, what about the aim?"},{"time":234430,"text":"The aim is to have more trust."},{"time":237050,"text":"Well frankly, I think that's a stupid aim."},{"time":240379,"text":"It's not what I would aim at."},{"time":242326,"text":"I would aim to have more trust in the trustworthy"},{"time":245789,"text":"but not in the untrustworthy."},{"time":248806,"text":"In fact, I aim positively to try not to trust the untrustworthy."},{"time":255348,"text":"And I think, of those people who, for example,"},{"time":258960,"text":"placed their savings with the very aptly named Mr. Madoff,"},{"time":263661,"text":"who then made off with them,"},{"time":266300,"text":"and I think of them, and I think, well, yes,"},{"time":268630,"text":"too much trust."},{"time":270493,"text":"More trust is not an intelligent aim in this life."},{"time":274350,"text":"Intelligently placed and intelligently refused trust"},{"time":278344,"text":"is the proper aim."},{"time":280811,"text":"Well once one says that, one says, yeah, okay,"},{"time":284274,"text":"that means that what matters in the first place"},{"time":287418,"text":"is not trust but trustworthiness."},{"time":290559,"text":"It's judging how trustworthy people are"},{"time":293477,"text":"in particular respects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295406,"text":"And I think that judgment requires us to look at three things."},{"time":298754,"text":"Are they competent? Are they honest? Are they reliable?"},{"time":303966,"text":"And if we find that a person is competent"},{"time":306038,"text":"in the relevant matters,"},{"time":307774,"text":"and reliable and honest,"},{"time":309695,"text":"we'll have a pretty good reason to trust them,"},{"time":311989,"text":"because they'll be trustworthy."},{"time":314200,"text":"But if, on the other hand, they're unreliable, we might not."},{"time":317866,"text":"I have friends who are competent and honest,"},{"time":320110,"text":"but I would not trust them to post a letter,"},{"time":321897,"text":"because they're forgetful."},{"time":324469,"text":"I have friends who are very confident"},{"time":327141,"text":"they can do certain things,"},{"time":329104,"text":"but I realize that they overestimate their own competence."},{"time":333512,"text":"And I'm very glad to say, I don't think I have many friends"},{"time":336167,"text":"who are competent and reliable but extremely dishonest."},{"time":339801,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":340641,"text":"If so, I haven't yet spotted it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344028,"text":"But that's what we're looking for:"},{"time":346322,"text":"trustworthiness before trust."},{"time":348520,"text":"Trust is the response."},{"time":350428,"text":"Trustworthiness is what we have to judge."},{"time":352768,"text":"And, of course, it's difficult."},{"time":354499,"text":"Across the last few decades, we've tried to construct"},{"time":357848,"text":"systems of accountability for all sorts of institutions"},{"time":361121,"text":"and professionals and officials and so on"},{"time":363217,"text":"that will make it easier for us to judge their trustworthiness."},{"time":367823,"text":"A lot of these systems have the converse effect."},{"time":371095,"text":"They don't work as they're supposed to."},{"time":372971,"text":"I remember I was talking with a midwife who said,"},{"time":377386,"text":"\"Well, you see, the problem is it takes longer"},{"time":379718,"text":"to do the paperwork than to deliver the baby.\""},{"time":383219,"text":"And all over our public life, our institutional life,"},{"time":386990,"text":"we find that problem,"},{"time":388840,"text":"that the system of accountability"},{"time":391253,"text":"that is meant to secure trustworthiness"},{"time":393582,"text":"and evidence of trustworthiness"},{"time":396332,"text":"is actually doing the opposite."},{"time":398196,"text":"It is distracting people who have to do difficult tasks,"},{"time":402833,"text":"like midwives, from doing them"},{"time":405146,"text":"by requiring them to tick the boxes, as we say."},{"time":408104,"text":"You can all give your own examples there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410838,"text":"So so much for the aim."},{"time":412748,"text":"The aim, I think, is more trustworthiness,"},{"time":415638,"text":"and that is going to be different"},{"time":417797,"text":"if we are trying to be trustworthy"},{"time":419746,"text":"and communicate our trustworthiness to other people,"},{"time":422772,"text":"and if we are trying to judge whether other people"},{"time":425676,"text":"or office-holders or politicians are trustworthy."},{"time":428848,"text":"It's not easy. It is judgment, and simple reaction,"},{"time":433222,"text":"attitudes, don't do adequately here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438084,"text":"Now thirdly, the task."},{"time":441649,"text":"Calling the task rebuilding trust, I think,"},{"time":445221,"text":"also gets things backwards."},{"time":446960,"text":"It suggests that you and I should rebuild trust."},{"time":451815,"text":"Well, we can do that for ourselves."},{"time":454268,"text":"We can rebuild a bit of trustworthiness."},{"time":456666,"text":"We can do it two people together trying to improve trust."},{"time":460298,"text":"But trust, in the end, is distinctive"},{"time":463502,"text":"because it's given by other people."},{"time":466262,"text":"You can't rebuild what other people give you."},{"time":469439,"text":"You have to give them the basis"},{"time":472166,"text":"for giving you their trust."},{"time":475349,"text":"So you have to, I think, be trustworthy."},{"time":478541,"text":"And that, of course, is because you can't fool"},{"time":480925,"text":"all of the people all of the time, usually."},{"time":484511,"text":"But you also have to provide usable evidence"},{"time":489157,"text":"that you are trustworthy."},{"time":490711,"text":"How to do it?"},{"time":492253,"text":"Well every day, all over the place, it's being done"},{"time":495463,"text":"by ordinary people, by officials, by institutions,"},{"time":498477,"text":"quite effectively."},{"time":500317,"text":"Let me give you a simple commercial example."},{"time":503830,"text":"The shop where I buy my socks says I may take them back,"},{"time":507720,"text":"and they don't ask any questions."},{"time":509972,"text":"They take them back and give me the money"},{"time":511733,"text":"or give me the pair of socks of the color I wanted."},{"time":514365,"text":"That's super. I trust them"},{"time":516554,"text":"because they have made themselves vulnerable to me."},{"time":519885,"text":"I think there's a big lesson in that."},{"time":521878,"text":"If you make yourself vulnerable to the other party,"},{"time":524932,"text":"then that is very good evidence that you are trustworthy"},{"time":528835,"text":"and you have confidence in what you are saying."},{"time":531853,"text":"So in the end, I think what we are aiming for"},{"time":534025,"text":"is not very difficult to discern."},{"time":537565,"text":"It is relationships in which people are trustworthy"},{"time":541770,"text":"and can judge when and how the other person"},{"time":545645,"text":"is trustworthy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546933,"text":"So the moral of all this is,"},{"time":550791,"text":"we need to think much less about trust,"},{"time":553945,"text":"let alone about attitudes of trust"},{"time":557480,"text":"detected or mis-detected by opinion polls,"},{"time":561166,"text":"much more about being trustworthy,"},{"time":563780,"text":"and how you give people adequate, useful"},{"time":567685,"text":"and simple evidence that you're trustworthy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570429,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571490,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}